{"tid":1728771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 教育局宣佈明天全港學校繼續停課","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:49:55.000Z","uid":276827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a601692f2efe2759ed87a00df5e183d46a7ee0","tid":1728771,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"#最新消息 <br />\n1202 教育局宣佈明天全港學校繼續停課"},{"pid":"3e5578cdf98cb2c1645ef7ae09f6c3676ad4e55a","tid":1728771,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b972a03045b788c67c4e9e8754086179c0888b56","tid":1728771,"uid":311098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"又中圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ef630ce728fd56c99d590b79c570ab3c6e87cf","tid":1728771,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］ 係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6121f14dbee379e5a37843092ac105b8ec0cd8b","tid":1728771,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"教育局特別宣布 <br />\n<br />\n雖然 *全港道路及公共運輸服務逐步恢復，但目前尚有不穩定因素，而星期一亦是周末後第一個繁忙的工作日* ，基於安全考慮，全港學校（包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校）明日（十一月十八日）繼續停課， *並應為日後復課作好準備* 。<br />\n<br />\n停課期間，學校必須保持校舍開放，家長如有需要可將子女送返學校。學校應安排教職員在安全可行的情況下返回學校照顧學生，與家長保持溝通，並在安全的情況下方可安排學生返家。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各界</span></span>應立刻停止一切暴力破壞活動，讓學生可以恢復正常的學校生活。如情況許可，學校最快將於星期二（十一月十九日）復課，請留意教育局進一步公布，學校應為復課做好準備，因應各種突發情況，就上課安排擬定校本應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n教育局再次提醒學生應留在家中，不要在街上流連，遠離危險，更切勿參加違法活動。"},{"pid":"061b0023fe83022711863fd1a7ff944dc1c43b8a","tid":1728771,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"又中"},{"pid":"5ca61da7ed6b74087593ed57b2db19f7d6a8daf1","tid":1728771,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"繼續交個波比警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402cf8c7fc25daad1537dd2705d76b8c4f9ee4d1","tid":1728771,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"27f7f8e4427f4ae928eb59ed34a65316d5eb15a9","tid":1728771,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b972a03045b788c67c4e9e8754086179c0888b56","tid":1728771,"uid":311098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"又中圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"林奠真係好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76aa95629423cd38071f2ad9335bd7bbfa11929","tid":1728771,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca61da7ed6b74087593ed57b2db19f7d6a8daf1","tid":1728771,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"繼續交個波比警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"要吹風係政府令到停課局面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}